      "source": [
        "{",
        "   # connect to given host or use 'active' to connect to the active debugged process",
        "   connection: active ",
        "   envs : {",
        "       default: {sandbox:false},",
        "       uie : {connection: \"localhost:8081\", sandbox:true},",
        "       xs : {connection: \"localhost:8080\"},",
        "   }",
        "}"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "markup",
      "language": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "# Sample xsbook",
        "",
        "Ez az xsbook egy-ket uj fejlesztest hivatott prezentalni.",
        "",
        "## Object info",
        "",
        "Data es objectekeet reszletei kattintasra kibonthatoak, forrashoz lehet ugrani.",
        "",
        "Definialjunk egy kis adatot"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "language": "xsmixed",
      "source": [
        "/// env:uie",
        "odict data {",
        "    arr = [ 1,2,3,10];",
        "    value = 1,2,3;",
        "    app = [odict {",
        "            name=\"cokcpit\";",
        "            path=\"c:/work/cockpit\"",
        "        },",
        "        odict {",
        "            name=\"uie\";",
        "            path=\"c:/work/nsdk/..\"",
        "    }];",
        "    emb = class {",
        "        static name = \"embedded class\";",
        "        prop = 42;",
        "    }",
        "};"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "markup",
      "language": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "Vizsgaljuk meg az adatot, erre tobb lehetoseg is van",
        "* return value-t ki lehet bontani",
        "* console.log debugerben megszokott modon kibonthato adatokat eredmenyez",
        "* console.dir az adatrol snapshotot keszit, mindig a dir hivasakor "
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "language": "xsmixed",
      "source": [
        "/// env:uie",
        "console.log(\"apps\", data);",
        "data.emb"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "markup",
      "language": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## console.dir",
        "",
        "Console.dir snapshotok keszit, azaz lemasolja az adatot es azt az allapotot mutatja amikor kiadtuk a `dir` hivast.",
        "",
        "Mig `console.log` allapota atto fugg mikor kertuk le"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "language": "xsmixed",
      "source": [
        "console.dir(\"dir\", data);",
        "console.log(\"log\", data);",
        "data.extra = 42;",
        "console.dir(\"dir extra adattal:\", data)"
      ]
    },
