      "kind": "markup",
      "language": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## UI Events",
        "",
        "Uj UI eventetket lehet definialni `defineEvent` reven. Ezekre a szokasos `addEventListener`-rel lehet feliratkozni.<br>",
        "Widgetekre az `on<EventName>` property segitsevel egyszerusitett feliratkozas lehetseges (bubble es target fazisban for felhivodni)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "language": "xsmixed",
      "source": [
        "import {CustomEvent, defineEvent} from \"system://ui.core\"",
        "{}",
        "defineEvent(@kutya); // onKutya"
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "code",
      "language": "xsmixed",
      "source": [
        "import {CustomEvent, defineEvent} from \"system://ui.core\"",
        "{}",
        "defineEvent(@kutya); // onLokutya",
        "screen.onKutya = (e) => { console.log(\"receiveed kutya event\", e.detail, e.currentTarget); console.dir(e);};",
        "screen.root.firstChild.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent(@kutya, #{detail: 42}));"
      ]
    },
